    <item>
      <title>埃及在国际货币基金组织协议后削减支出，上调燃油价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/egypt-hikes-fuel-prices-in-latest-spending-cut-after-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及将多种燃料产品价格上调高达 15%，这是该国与国际货币基金组织达成新协议后最新一次政府补贴削减举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/egypt-hikes-fuel-prices-in-latest-spending-cut-after-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师称黎智英将在香港国安​​案审判中作证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/hong-kong-court-rejects-jimmy-lai-s-bid-to-drop-security-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港民主派大亨黎智英将出庭为自己辩护，此案与一起重大国家安全案件有关。此前，法庭驳回了黎智英提出的撤销指控的请求，这位 76 岁老人可能因此被判终身监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/hong-kong-court-rejects-jimmy-lai-s-bid-to-drop-security-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:47:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制裁加剧，俄罗斯企业面临越来越多的付款问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/russian-companies-face-mounting-payment-issues-as-sanctions-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京不顾西方国家在国际上孤立他的企图，自 5 月以来与 20 多位世界领导人举行了会晤。俄罗斯企业就没那么幸运了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/russian-companies-face-mounting-payment-issues-as-sanctions-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国推迟对越南市场经济地位作出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-delays-decision-on-vietnam-s-market-economy-status-by-a-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府宣布是否将越南列为市场经济的决定的时间已延长一周，将于 8 月 2 日之前公布，此举可能促进越南的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-delays-decision-on-vietnam-s-market-economy-status-by-a-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:14:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡为以色列与哈马斯的战争进行激烈辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/netanyahu-tells-congress-us-and-israel-must-stand-together</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本雅明内塔尼亚胡在美国国会发表演讲，为以色列与哈马斯的战争进行激烈辩护，将自己置身于美国政坛的紧张时刻，并嘲笑国会外数千名抗议其对加沙冲突处理方式的示威者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/netanyahu-tells-congress-us-and-israel-must-stand-together</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 18:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚银行被要求就暴利外汇收益缴纳 70% 的税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/-ngn-usd-nigerian-banks-asked-to-pay-70-tax-on-windfall-forex-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为充实国库，尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布最初提议对银行的外汇收益征收 50% 的税，而议会批准了这一计划，将税率从 50% 提高到 70%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/-ngn-usd-nigerian-banks-asked-to-pay-70-tax-on-windfall-forex-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:40:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
